      "reviewTitle": "性价比高，推荐。Cost-effective, highly recommended.!",
      "originalTitle": "",
      "originalComment": "",
      "reviewComments": "酒店干净整洁，员工非常友好，主动打招呼和提供服务，进门有工作人员帮忙拎包。前台温柔专业，房间干净整洁，毛巾柔软舒适，洗澡有热水，有牙刷牙膏提供。旁边有大型超市，有街边美食摊。特别推荐天台自助早餐，可以品尝当地风味美食，粥、面、主食、甜品和水果。顺便说一下，Hotel  Manager very handsome!\n\nThe hotel is clean and tidy, the staff is very friendly, take the initiative to greet and provide services, the door staff to help carry bags. The front desk is gentle and professional, the room is clean and tidy, the towel is soft and comfortable, the bath has hot water, toothbrush and toothpaste are provided. Next to a large supermarket, there are street food stalls. The rooftop breakfast buffet is especially recommended. You can enjoy local delicacies such as congee, noodles, staple foods, desserts and fruits. By the way, Hotel Manager very handsome!Highly recommend!",
